      <h2 id="About_Us">About us</h2>
      <p>What about the WILD CIRCUS? Come discover the most spectacular circus in Indre-et-Loir. </br>
        Since 1994, The WILD CIRCUS let children and adults dream during a new show every year during two hours!!
      Low prices, good seats, incredible show and delicious pop-corn are the definition of The WILD CIRCUS. </p>
